Package net.emuman.spigotutils.armorstands

Class ArmorStandLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.Location
      • net.emuman.spigotutils.armorstands.ArmorStandLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable
    public class ArmorStandLocation
extends org.bukkit.Location
    Represents the location of an armor stand object/model in space, including world, pitch, yaw, and roll. This does NOT represent the actual location of the armor stand, but the location of the associated object/model.
